<Document>
  <name>Nacogdoches County — Unmapped Historical Markers</name>
  <description>THC markers in Nacogdoches County without an HMDB id (isMissing excluded). 21 with THC coords; 0 geocoded from address; 16 omitted (no usable address).</description>
  <Placemark>
    <name>100th Anniversary of Oil in Nacogdoches County</name>
    <description><![CDATA[across from Old Stone Fort on Griffith &amp; Alumni, SFA Campus<br/><br/><b>Address:</b> Nacogdoches<br/><br/><b>Marker Text:</b> --]]></description>
